## Limitations

This report is based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on vaccination. The information is current as of the last update in October 2023, and new developments in vaccine research and public health policies may not be reflected. Additionally, the report focuses on general reasons for vaccination and may not address specific concerns or contraindications for certain populations.